Selected accessible datasets for AI improvement:

Primary dry-eye dataset:
- Tear Meniscus Segmentation Dataset for Dry Eye Diagnosis
- Link: https://figshare.com/articles/dataset/Tear_Meniscus_Segmentation_for_Dry_Eye_Diagnosis/

Alternative public ocular dataset:
- APTOS 2019 Blindness Detection Dataset (Kaggle)
- Link: https://www.kaggle.com/c/aptos2019-blindness-detection

Note: ODIR-5K has been removed from the draft because it is a challenge-style dataset with registration and does not clearly offer a larger unexplored improvement margin than these public options.